{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in <i>Tome of Fates</i>, an Adventure Gamebook: create, play, and share unique stories through the built-in story editor. Play solo or co-op with friends, craft epic narratives without any coding, then share them on the Steam Workshop for others to enjoy.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EDITOR - Story Creation, Simplified</h2></li></ul>Dive into the powerful yet intuitive story editor. This tool allows you to design branching narratives without any programming knowledge, making it easy to bring your imagination to life.<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310150/extras/Page_header.jpg?t=1731986688\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WORKSHOP- Share Your Stories</h2></li></ul>Share your stories on Steam Workshop and discover new adventures from the community.<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310150/extras/Page_header2.jpg?t=1731986688\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MULTIPLAYER - Co-op / Twitch viewer interaction</h2></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don't want to play alone? Our unique CO-OP system allows you and your chosen friends to vote on the path the story takes and what choices to make. Bit of a streamer? Use our Twitch Integration system to allow viewers to join in on the fun and influence your story! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310150/extras/BG3_3.jpg?t=1731986688\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Founding Member","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2310150/e32805aee421d2fb74504fb3e8360e35c611a44d.jpg"},{"name":"Death is only the begining","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/